name: Thankful Mirror
description:
This is a mirrored and continuous picture of previous mint called But are you Thankful.

As it is written there staying thankful might melt away, and when you keep on flying around errands and rushing to next thing and or going too slow you will just see those things. And thankfulness is just gone.

Learn to not be hypnotized by what you just desire but stay thankful afloat and with overview.
